(1)	 The Prime Minister must establish the Namibia Vulnerability Assessment Committee which consists of the following members appointed by the Prime Minister after consultation with the Committee -
* a staff member from the Office of the Prime Minister of at least deputy director level in the public service who is the chairperson;
